t it is not the event averaging that creates the non-Gaussian features\nin the pair distributions. Based on this observation, we determine\nL\\'evy-parameters of the source as a function of event centrality and particle\nmomentum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2022 02:46:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Oct 2022 13:54:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-04"}
