tmospheric parameters and metal abundances\nprovide overwhelming evidence for the double-degenerate merger scenario.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2022 12:38:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Jan 2022 14:32:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-09"}
