ples of subfields of No stable by exponential and\nlogarithmic functions, and does not require to go up to a cardinal {\\lambda} to\nprovide such examples.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 20 Jan 2022 14:28:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-21"}
